snippet.textDisplay:
Sorry guys, first/only video I've disliked of yours, and first of ANY I've bothered to in years, but... we need the ratio # to draw your attention to this, so hopefully it will be recognized that we, the fans, DO NOT WANT TO SEE RAID:SL HERE, or any other such predatory/harmful spyware/malware software promoted here. You claim to only use brand sponsors you trust, and.... if THAT's who you trust, how can we trust you? If you'd sell your viewers' privacy/financial stability/livelihood/etc all for a sponsor payout? How can we trust that you're not also being paid by some shady CCP-run hardware manufacturer, and all the switches you recommend don't have a secret level0 back door written into the firmware? 
Please, Linus and the LTT/Techlinked team, PLEASE don't do this. Don't just sell out and become yet another untrustworthy shill channel, leaving us all to go search again for a tech-reviewer we can trust.
